# Data Visualization

## Components

### Map View

- Show current positions of bikes, allow to see current status (borrowed/free, speed, ...)
- Show different zones on a map (restricted areas, boundaries)
- Inspect historical data
    - Of individual bikes (ride history)
    - Heatmap of all bikes in certain timeframe

### Fleet Overview

- List of all bikes in fleet, showing their status, highlighting alerts
- Show further details of individual bike (usage %, total km, average km a day, raw historical data, ...)
- Show aggregated values for whole fleet
- What do we do with the parking stations?